      <title>Kitten Flea Treatment (Video)</title>
      <link>http://fleacontrolsecrets.com/fleatreatment/natural-flea-control/kitten-flea-treatment-video/</link>
      <comments>http://fleacontrolsecrets.com/fleatreatment/natural-flea-control/kitten-flea-treatment-video/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Oct 2009 02:55:13 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>FleaControlSecrets</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Cats and Fleas]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Natural Flea Control]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[cat flea comb]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[kitten flea treatment]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://fleacontrolsecrets.com/fleatreatment/?p=318</guid>
      <description>Using flea treatment on kittens under 8 weeks of age is not recommended. This video shows how to use a flea comb to get rid of fleas and determine if a kitten has a flea infestation. Large numbers of fleas can endanger kittens due to flea bite anemia and a veterinary visit is always recommended [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/flea-control-secrets-how-to-get-rid-of-fleas-live/Flea_Control_Secrets-_How_To_Get_Rid_of_Fleas__Liv-Kitten_Flea_Treatment_Video.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
